{"tid":49752,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打屙屎識壓水花","createTime":"2016-12-22T02:37:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T03:51:03.000Z","uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e4e2ff232b3b642909568e5af89a4d04a3061ba5","tid":49752,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:37:05.000Z","msg":"彈到成個屎忽都係水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e861c6b4a2f0627ef304e9ee37ae2ae7ae912c35","tid":49752,"uid":7824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:39:28.000Z","msg":"彈到成個屎忽都係屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8d56f711dc1c458454318b6508fbe2717a7d57","tid":49752,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:40:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>彈到成個屎忽都係屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f5b462ff06f95964df27cbded6bd21358825b19","tid":49752,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:41:22.000Z","msg":"每次屙屎都會用手接住再慢慢放落馬桶，等d屎係水中整齊d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd0c26c9e3f5a17ad210e19dbbfcd01825f5b25","tid":49752,"uid":29203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b42552790a9a033cb6354110ba1c2f1cb48d7151","tid":49752,"uid":17348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:41:53.000Z","msg":"鋪紙巾落啲水到咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60486016c3e2264bdc49062c63577ef93d059c5b","tid":49752,"uid":38492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:42:39.000Z","msg":"我會放啲紙巾先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c1fd707089f7b04df0b1c11903cbdbca2df7e3","tid":49752,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:43:24.000Z","msg":"鋪定紙巾是常識吧"},{"pid":"2b3461581020f8dffc32819e481d5ba3681f9795","tid":49752,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:43:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鋪紙巾落啲水到咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁唔環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d958e30d055ec00220ff77d49d02c41919a706ce","tid":49752,"uid":4360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:54:03.000Z","msg":"屙屎唔壓水花你不如唔好屙"},{"pid":"7c66ab08345af2ac068159d49a2737a69d433e7f","tid":49752,"uid":25099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:54:32.000Z","msg":"假設你痾既屎係長而實<br />\n1. 鐘擺原理 (Pendulum Effect)<br />\n臨痾斷果下屎忽要前後擺動,<br />\n利用鐘擺原理, 屎忽向前時,將條屎起垂直一刻用肛門括約肌夾斷<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.flickr.com/234/524044416_f9ca845c72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.flickr.com%2F234%2F524044416_f9ca845c72.jpg&h=13b00cf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁條屎就會有慣性同動能向馬桶前方飛,<br />\n應該會撻中馬桶前, 賓周對落既位置, 然後慢慢sir 返落堆水度,<br />\n做到咁應該係0水花<br />\n<br />\n2. 游繩垂落 (Perpendicular Abseiling)<br />\n痾屎果陣要確定你條屎既粗度係一致, 盡量唔好夾斷條屎, <br />\n等條屎可以好似游繩咁慢慢沉入水裡面, <br />\n呢個時候你可以夾斷條屎,<br />\n條屎應該會有垂直方式插入水中, <br />\n好似奧運跳水咁做到0水花,<br />\n加上條屎一早已經掂住水面, 唔會破壞到水面既張力,<br />\n水花更細<br />\n<br />\n如果你痾既係爛屎/ 一粒粒既屎<br />\n1. 破壞性干擾(destructive interference)<br />\n當你第一粒屎果刻, 粒屎掉水面會造成漣漪, 漣漪撞到馬桶邊後會反彈,<br />\n你要計算好反彈既波長同波度, 將第二粒屎痾落去造做破壞性干擾<br />\n<img src=\"http://www2.mcdaniel.edu/Biology/PGclass/hearing%20noise/intrfrnc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.mcdaniel.edu%2FBiology%2FPGclass%2Fhearing%2520noise%2Fintrfrnc.gif&h=16f22f68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如上圖左, 咁兩個WAVE 就會互相抵消, 水面會非常平靜, <br />\n但你如果計錯, 造做180度既相差, 就會出現constructive interference,<br />\n到時水花就會以2倍既威力彈起, 你屎忽就瀨晒野.<br />\n<br />\n最後, practice makes perfect. 共勉之"},{"pid":"6e409e57e216dd4b0126d6900fe80eb8a6727142","tid":49752,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:55:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屙屎唔壓水花你不如唔好屙</blockquote><br />\n所以咪問囉<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Le92d7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLe92d7.gif&h=2409b48a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dee40be0d9d9e2834c49fe12c80c8050cb2e2607","tid":49752,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:58:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>假設你痾既屎係長而實<br />\n1. 鐘擺原理 (Pendulum Effect)<br />\n臨痾斷果下屎忽要前後擺動,<br />\n利用鐘擺原理, 屎忽向前時,將條屎起垂直一刻用肛門括約肌夾斷<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.flickr.com/234/524044416_f9ca845c72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.flickr.com%2F234%2F524044416_f9ca845c72.jpg&h=13b00cf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁條屎就會有慣性同動能向馬桶前方飛,<br />\n應該會撻中馬桶前, 賓周對落既位置, 然後慢慢sir 返落堆水度,<br />\n做到咁應該係0水花<br />\n<br />\n2. 游繩垂落 (Perpendicular Abseiling)<br />\n痾屎果陣要確定你條屎既粗度係一致, 盡量唔好夾斷條屎, <br />\n等條屎可以好似游繩咁慢慢沉入水裡面, <br />\n呢個時候你可以夾斷條屎,<br />\n條屎應該會有垂直方式插入水中, <br />\n好似奧運跳水咁做到0水花,<br />\n加上條屎一早已經掂住水面, 唔會破壞到水面既張力,<br />\n水花更細<br />\n<br />\n如果你痾既係爛屎/ 一粒粒既屎<br />\n1. 破壞性干擾(destructive interference)<br />\n當你第一粒屎果刻, 粒屎掉水面會造成漣漪, 漣漪撞到馬桶邊後會反彈,<br />\n你要計算好反彈既波長同波度, 將第二粒屎痾落去造做破壞性干擾<br />\n<img src=\"http://www2.mcdaniel.edu/Biology/PGclass/hearing%20noise/intrfrnc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.mcdaniel.edu%2FBiology%2FPGclass%2Fhearing%2520noise%2Fintrfrnc.gif&h=16f22f68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如上圖左, 咁兩個WAVE 就會互相抵消, 水面會非常平靜, <br />\n但你如果計錯, 造做180度既相差, 就會出現constructive interference,<br />\n到時水花就會以2倍既威力彈起, 你屎忽就瀨晒野.<br />\n<br />\n最後, practice makes perfect. 共勉之</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n練左２鳩幾年都成日有ＷＡＶＥ<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20fefb23381f95fcc3e883d04b30f5999d06024","tid":49752,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:59:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鋪紙巾落啲水到咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁唔環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但呢個方法係work"},{"pid":"b25f15a4d7c19c691194b6060b94ac80fb15dc76","tid":49752,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T03:00:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鋪紙巾落啲水到咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁唔環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但呢個方法係work</blockquote><br />\n次次一急就坐左落去,咩都無準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f45131971b778691807d6c1dcf90affc30a41409","tid":49752,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T03:30:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鋪紙巾落啲水到咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁唔環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但呢個方法係work</blockquote><br />\n次次一急就坐左落去,咩都無準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一屙出黎果下禁水沖廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e997bdebfd1584d196bebcc93eeadbcab1eb40d","tid":49752,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T03:44:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ecdd82e8d16e98218bb6c8a5ecd09defe1d1f281","tid":49752,"uid":50842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T03:51:03.000Z","msg":"個屎忽坐落d，屎眼浸係水痾"}]}